5️⃣ One Important Thing

When you run:

php artisan make:filament-resource User

Laravel will ask:

Generate for existing model? (yes/no)

Type:

yes

Because User model already exists.

6️⃣ Correct Order For Filament Commands

Run them like this:

Role
User
Seller
Buyer
Item
Sale
7️⃣ After That

You will implement:

role permissions

menu access control

P&L report

These are the actual assignment requirements.

✅ So answer: Yes, you should run those Filament commands after migrations.
